%% Diagram: Fragment piercing — incrementally migrate a legacy SPA via edge fragments
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant Edge as Edge Worker (Gateway)
    participant Legacy as Legacy SPA (origin)
    participant Frag as New Fragment (origin)

    U->>Edge: GET /account
    Edge->>Legacy: Fetch shell HTML
    Edge->>Frag: Fetch new fragment HTML in parallel
    Frag-->>Edge: SSR fragment (interactive at first paint)
    Legacy-->>Edge: Shell HTML
    Edge-->>U: Stream shell + fragment at top of DOM
    Note over U: Fragment is interactive immediately
    U->>U: Legacy SPA hydrates
    U->>U: Pierce: move fragment node into\n<piercing-fragment-outlet>
    Note over U: No layout shift · focus and form state preserved
